the event bus. The real data component uses its own API-matched type from the hook.\n\nBut wait, the checklist explicitly requires updating `ProfileTransaction` to match the API shape with an `event` field and renaming `outcome` to `event`. The old type has `outcome: \"win\" | \"loss\"`, while the new API includes `event: \"join\" | \"win\" | \"loss\" | \"refund\"`. I need to update the type definition to reflect this change, mapping `gameId` from the API's `game` field.\n\nDefining the updated type...\n\nUpdating mock-simulation to use the new shape...","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1368,"cache_read_input_tokens":57162,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1368},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6352b9d5-eba7-498a-a945-ee2c953d2486","uuid":"469cf1d2-0be3-43b7-ad39-8f28e421dfaf"}
